{"tid":437961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"反耶反上腦？","createTime":"2017-10-16T12:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T08:07:37.000Z","uid":148934,"like":10,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"81afeb00c04d1cd08b8132ac65a81d41c13a3d8a","tid":437961,"uid":148934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"老老實實大把宗教俾你地去追擊，點睇都唔係耶教先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到隔離post話咩耶教虛偽，十惡不赦咁，但係教會做嘅好事就隻字不提，係咩道理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你就咁話信埋啲故事書弱智我都明，但反到上晒腦同isis比係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58cf8e184b9436a0e6d78dc4f487e837eee557c6","tid":437961,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765f222dabfc0bed5b4dc189615f9a86d2f82df0","tid":437961,"uid":139349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:49:38.000Z","msg":"信耶本身就係無腦行為"},{"pid":"b2feedb3508df854a255b3e5509865b3edbb6279","tid":437961,"uid":59465,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:49:52.000Z","msg":"教會做好事定壞事我唔知<br />\n<br />\n但係耶教就一定係教壞人<br />\n<br />\n違反邏輯 盲目祟拜 指鹿為馬<br />\n<br />\n令成個社會倒退"},{"pid":"c56585e058eadb3fa6d44fb222609b394198f880","tid":437961,"uid":59465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:51:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>信耶本身就係無腦行為</blockquote><br />\n古時會信唔出奇<br />\n當時宗教仲有教化作用令平民變得容易管理<br />\n因為可以消滅平民嘅獨立思考能力<br />\n<br />\n但係依家咩年代呀？<br />\n人人有書讀 可以上網睇想睇嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n但仲係咁多人迷信宗教 星座<br />\n真係好可悲"},{"pid":"0789b62c6de1692427fc7ac7deaf58fef16c1559","tid":437961,"uid":125419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:53:42.000Z","msg":"但係殺人放火佢做過晒bor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79fa700f0ccd6f6b27e8d4e61b3becaeb40bb829","tid":437961,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"咪由得佢哋活在自己啲世界囉<br />\n世界人口估咗幾多基督徙？<br />\n基督教平日做咗幾善事，幫助幾多人？<br />\n佢哋最多咪網上鍵國、發up瘋做個怨婦<br />\n乜都反 人種、肥婆、身高、職業<br />\n始終呢班人難成大器"},{"pid":"060c588300cf9df2e0a30fb44b039715ca038278","tid":437961,"uid":148934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係殺人放火佢做過晒bor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樹大有枯枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7496c5d2b0c98aebb01198d87f9a0a6f47ca549c","tid":437961,"uid":148934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:53:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教會做好事定壞事我唔知<br />\n<br />\n但係耶教就一定係教壞人<br />\n<br />\n違反邏輯 盲目祟拜 指鹿為馬<br />\n<br />\n令成個社會倒退</blockquote><br />\n如果你知道左教會做好多好事 會唔會改觀？"},{"pid":"59eda5110816dc2f6c363f3bc582d551fd23612d","tid":437961,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:18:28.000Z","msg":"信耶信上腦?"},{"pid":"4784251ff4ba1e8940fe06958a87968f4a9256ab","tid":437961,"uid":125419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但係殺人放火佢做過晒bor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樹大有枯枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我指神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ebb7cf754efdd81fd7b2d4d9ee36f0ccd0b7911","tid":437961,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:43:15.000Z","msg":"最簡易反耶冇生命危險<br />\n反伊會死人的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc66caa5ad2149078c9c405994b8a65f39963e0","tid":437961,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"耶撚食屎大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p